basis.applyingPolicies: . Automated QA must be possible: Measure 'automated QA supported' must have a value equal true . Format Documentation freely available: Measure 'format documentation availability' should have a value equal yes-free . Comparative file size must be less then 10: Measure 'comparative file size' must have a value lower than 10 . Action software licence must be open source: Measure 'software licence source code' must have a value equal openSource . Format should be international standard: Measure 'format standardization' should have a value equal international standard . Ease of integration: Measure 'ease of integration' should have a value equal good . Number of tools greater 0: Measure 'number of tools' must have a value greater than 0 . Elapsed time per MB: Measure 'elapsed time per MB' must have a value lower than 2000 . Image width must be unchanged: Measure 'image width equal' must have a value equal true . Action tool usability should be good: Measure 'ease of use' should have a value equal openSource . Quantitative archival storage costs: Measure 'quantitative archival storage costs' must have a value lower than 0.24 . Action should be stable: Measure 'stability judgement' should have a value equal stable . Identification possibilities must be automatic: Measure 'identification possibilities' must have a value equal automatic_specific . Image height must be unchanged: Measure 'image height equal' must have a value equal true . Compression type must be none: Measure 'compression type' must have a value equal none . All Tiff data must be retained: Measure 'EXIF: all tiff data retained' must have a value equal true . Colour model must be preserved: Measure 'colour model preserved' must have a value equal true . Format complexity should be low: Measure 'format complexity' should have a value equal low . Running costs per object: Measure 'Running costs per object' must have a value lower than 0.24
